1031
01:19:49,638 --> 01:19:51,960
have gone unfulfilled by the city administration.

1032
01:19:52,560 --> 01:20:00,946
Be it resolved that the city solicitor provide the council with a draft ordinance requiring that the council be provided with the warrant articles on a monthly basis.

1033
01:20:01,666 --> 01:20:10,812
And be it further resolved that the city solicitor send a freedom of information request to the city administration on behalf of the city council requesting the following information.

1034
01:20:11,452 --> 01:20:14,454
Copies of all warrant articles for the period of January 1st,

1035
01:20:18,178 --> 01:20:19,540
Mr. President, thank you very much.

1036
01:20:20,200 --> 01:20:25,807
As you're well aware, and my council colleagues are, the Warren articles are actually a copy of the bills that we pay at the end of every month.

1037
01:20:26,468 --> 01:20:33,056
And when we talk about transparency in government, one of the things we always hear is, follow the dollar, follow the dollar.

1038
01:20:33,536 --> 01:20:43,600
And I think it's very important, Mr. President, if we are going to be a transparent community financially with an open checkbook, that this council is made aware of where the money is being spent and when it's being spent.

1039
01:20:44,320 --> 01:20:48,682
For example, our vendors that are providing testing for COVID-19.

1040
01:20:49,642 --> 01:20:50,222
have to get paid?

1041
01:20:50,682 --> 01:20:51,322
Are they being paid?

1042
01:20:51,542 --> 01:20:52,263
Do they have a balance?

1043
01:20:52,963 --> 01:20:54,683
How much money have we invested in COVID testing?

1044
01:20:54,723 --> 01:20:57,064
Is this money reimbursable through the CARES Act or the HEROES Act?

1045
01:20:57,684 --> 01:21:02,445
This is good information for us, Mr. President, to have to make solid, strong financial decisions moving forward.

1046
01:21:03,085 --> 01:21:09,427
So absent the fact that multiple requests have gone unanswered, I do think that this is a good legislative

1047
01:21:10,638 --> 01:21:16,460
