01:29:27,510 --> 01:29:33,713
Earlier this evening when our meeting opened up, we started off with a public hearing relative to a grant of location on Mitchell Ave.

1164
01:29:34,473 --> 01:29:43,478
And the procedure was we call the public hearing to order, we read it into the record, and then we ask if people are opposed to or in favor of the project that's before us.

1165
01:29:44,512 --> 01:29:45,714
Then we close the public hearing.

1166
01:29:45,734 --> 01:29:52,602
Then we allow the petitioner to provide us with a presentation as to what the project's going to be.

1167
01:29:54,966 --> 01:30:00,713
