1171
01:30:26,208 --> 01:30:30,530
Then we're turning the floor over to the developer, or the applicant, I should say,

1172
01:30:31,010 --> 01:30:34,452
And the applicant gives a presentation, the council asks questions, and then we vote on it.

1173
01:30:35,132 --> 01:30:41,075
