1590
02:00:12,985 --> 02:00:14,586
Nobody's trying to put people in the street.

1591
02:00:15,007 --> 02:00:19,930
Housing Court has reached out to the realtor industry, and they are recruiting hundreds.

1592
02:00:20,410 --> 02:00:25,696
across the state in order to mediate between the tenants and the landlords.

1593
02:00:26,156 --> 02:00:35,285
So when the landlord is able to access that federal money, part of getting that money is an agreement that they're not going to evict the tenant.

1594
02:00:35,485 --> 02:00:42,132
If it's just a money issue, if it's a legal issue that they're breaking the law and they're making people unsafe, I think that's a different situation.

1595
02:00:42,992 --> 02:00:49,780
But I am on the Housing Sustainability Task Force group there and it hasn't met since last May.

1596
02:00:49,940 --> 02:00:57,749
