1607
02:01:42,555 --> 02:01:44,735
Nobody really wants to put anybody in the street.

1608
02:01:45,195 --> 02:01:53,057
And a lot of our landlords in Medford, they're elderly people, and they're relying on the rent in order to actually live and buy their food.

1609
02:01:53,537 --> 02:01:58,479
So it's important that we can keep the resources there for everybody, the tenants and the landlords.

1610
02:01:58,939 --> 02:02:03,581
